OL,3,CPrison described as 'war zone' as
OL,4,Cinmate claims 'staff paid' to bring in
OL,5,Cdrugs
OL,7,FParc Prison in has been described as a
OL,8,F"war zone" by a current inmate.
OL,10,FDarren Williams said he feels unsafe
OL,11,Fin the prison, claiming there is a
OL,12,Flack of staff and prison officers are
OL,13,Fpaid to bring in drugs.
OL,15,FIt comes as at the prison between 27
OL,16,FFebruary and 19 March - police believe
OL,17,Ffour of the deaths were drug-related.
OL,19,FThe Prisons and Probation Ombudsman is
OL,20,Finvestigating the deaths.
