OL,4,Cinmate claims 'staff paid' to bring in
OL,5,Cdrugs
OL,7,FAn HMP Parc spokesperson has rejected
OL,8,FMr Williams' claims, saying there are
OL,9,Fstrategies in place to root out drugs
OL,10,Fand contraband, and health and safety
OL,11,Fis a priority.
OL,13,FThe spokesperson added the "vast
OL,14,Fmajority of their staff are honest and
OL,15,Fhardworking."
OL,17,FBut calling his parents from a
OL,18,Flandline in his cell, Darren says
OL,19,F"it's getting bad" inside the prison.
