OL,4,Cinmate claims 'staff paid' to bring in
OL,5,Cdrugs
OL,7,FOn the phone, the now 41-year-old,
OL,8,Fsaid: "It's like a war zone in here.
OL,9,FPeople are walking around with shanks
OL,10,Fjust to feel safe. You're more likely
OL,11,Fto get spice than toilet paper. That's
OL,12,Fhow bad things are.
OL,14,F"The staff are bringing the drugs in.
OL,15,FThat's how it's getting into the jail.
OL,16,FPeople are ripping the paper, smoking
OL,17,Fthe paper. And the effects is people
OL,18,Fare dying off it.
