OL,7,F"You hear it all the time that
OL,8,Fofficers are fed up with their job.
OL,9,FThey quite willingly say this to us.
OL,10,FSo, then a prisoner or drug dealer
OL,11,Fwill go to an officer and ask 'do you
OL,12,Fwant to earn some more money?'
OL,14,F"Staff get paid #2,500 each time it's
OL,15,Fbrought in. They're never going to
OL,16,Fstop it."
