OL,7,FParc Prison is one of the largest
OL,8,Fprisons in the UK. The Ministry of
OL,9,FJustice renewed its contract with G4S
OL,10,Fin 2022, which has managed the prison
OL,11,Fsince it opened in 1997.
OL,13,FIn response to Darren's statements, an
OL,14,FHMP Parc spokesperson said: "All
OL,15,Fprisoners are searched as they leave
OL,16,Ftheir accommodation and at their place
OL,17,Fof work or education."
