OL,7,FZack Griffiths is a former inmate of
OL,8,FParc Prison. He was first sent there
OL,9,Fin 2016 after being found guilty of
OL,10,Fconspiracy to supply Class A drugs.
OL,12,FMr Griffiths was released in 2020 but
OL,13,Flater recalled to prison, spending the
OL,14,Fend of 2023 behind bars.
OL,16,FWhen comparing his two stints in Parc
OL,17,FPrison, Mr Griffiths said: "I just
OL,18,Fhave some bad memories of being in
OL,19,Fthat jail. It just changed. How it's
OL,20,Frun, the management. They just created
OL,21,Fthis environment that's just toxic.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/14
