OL,7,F"Absolute chaos, especially when
OL,8,Fyou've got this regime that's
OL,9,Foperating on a 23-hour lockdown.
OL,11,F"I noticed that there was a huge
OL,12,Fuptake in the amount of drugs that
OL,13,Fwere available in that prison. We're
OL,14,Ftalking about fentanyl, these new
OL,15,Fopiate drugs.
OL,17,F"People are dying on these drugs and
OL,18,Fthis prison is failing to manage the
OL,19,Fproblem."
