OL,7,FMr Griffiths believes prison should be
OL,8,Fcentred on rehabilitation: "It's about
OL,9,Fgiving the people a good environment
OL,10,Fto make a positive change in their
OL,11,Flife. What you're actually getting,
OL,12,Fthey're not being rehabilitated.
OL,14,F"So you have to think these people are
OL,15,Fgoing to come out of prison, they're
OL,16,Fgoing to be back in your communities.
OL,17,FThe public expect that rehabilitation
OL,18,Fto exist. It's just not fair."
