OL,7,FAn HMP Parc spokesperson disputes
OL,8,Fthese claims saying: "The health and
OL,9,Fsafety of prisoners and staff is our
OL,10,Fnumber one priority and there are a
OL,11,Fbroad range of work and education
OL,12,Factivities to support rehabilitation.
OL,14,F"Purposeful activity on average
OL,15,Fexceeds 30 hours per week and those
OL,16,Fmen who are willing to engage, have
OL,17,Flonger periods out of their cells."
