OL,7,FKevin said: "It's frightening for
OL,8,Fparents. It must be absolutely
OL,9,Fterrifying for an inmate to have to go
OL,10,Fthrough this.
OL,12,F"For your son to ring you and say 'dad
OL,13,Fthere's been another death today'.
OL,14,FWhat's going to happen? What's next?
OL,15,FWho's next? I don't know."
OL,17,FThe prison spokesperson said anyone
OL,18,Fconcerned about the welfare of a
OL,19,Fprison can call a dedicated number to
OL,20,Freport their concerns.
